item.title: Forecasting Brent Crude Oil Price: Box-Jenkins Method
item.description: Introduction: Crude oil is almost the most important commodity in the world. It is widely considered to be the lifeblood of our modern life and the crucial driver behind the radical transformations in the global economy over the last decades.
